name: FARTMOMMY
description: FARTMOMMY ($FARTMOMMY) is a community-driven meme token launched on the Solana blockchain. It is part of the Fart Dynasty, which includes other notable meme tokens like FARTBOY and FARTGIRL. The project leverages viral meme culture and decentralized community engagement to build a fun, interactive ecosystem. While primarily a meme token, it fosters an enthusiastic holder base and aims to expand through community-driven initiatives and social engagement campaigns within the crypto space.
